snippet.title: Amber Alert-style communication system discussed to warn Texans of future widespread electric outage
snippet.description: “AT&T has already reached out and said that they think they have a fix where they want to be helpful,” said state Rep. Craig Goldman, R-Fort Worth. Read more about the proposed system here: https://www.wfaa.com/article/news/politics/inside-politics/amber-alert-communication-system-discussed-to-warn-texans-of-future-widespread-electric-outages/287-0a8e1895-1ae5-4edf-bf38-097956d73de7
